{"tid":1290560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係大家教育媽媽嘅好機會","createTime":"2019-07-06T14:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:24:19.000Z","uid":35587,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb10d49555404eb4d14d8ceb93ae76534b4dde3","tid":1290560,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"話說教育多年 媽媽本身少黃偏中立 抱怨佢生意差咗 但都會屌林鄭做得差 話我哋遊行係可以 同投票非保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n今日講屯公單嘢比佢知 呀伯派錢嘅事 啲大媽賣淫<br />\n 佢即刻勁認真 我就比埋啲片佢 話警察唔捉 政府唔理 <br />\n佢即刻勁嬲 話啲人咸濕成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警犬正仆街唔捉 我話啲大陸婆昆哂佢哋啲棺材本<br />\n女人一聽到呢啲咸濕呀伯同賣淫事就會勁著緊 沖完涼出嚟就見佢就開住個電視屌警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d4b60448f8ce8960465c01afc4a5b03fc14371","tid":1290560,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:07:07.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"5680b8dccbb7e30d94c9c68c95c9fce20b2343fb","tid":1290560,"uid":213463,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"發覺連登仔真係講得好有道理😁我決定同其他BK嘅JM一齊過黎連登同後生仔傾下計😚"},{"pid":"1f8aa0a59098fcb19947412afa3748452aa2751a","tid":1290560,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5680b8dccbb7e30d94c9c68c95c9fce20b2343fb","tid":1290560,"uid":213463,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:17:12.000Z","msg":"發覺連登仔真係講得好有道理😁我決定同其他BK嘅JM一齊過黎連登同後生仔傾下計😚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d352a6813ec84e4fae9eb54020ae1a8c101ca527","tid":1290560,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb52b5edb18d866af911c01767a76d2fdb2fdd3","tid":1290560,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"最佳時機  快啲助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"